briefDescription: ISO 9001-2008 Certified Tulsi Eye Hospital (TEH) is professionally managed Comprehensive Quality Eye Care provider in Northern Maharashtra, having state of the Art equipment, qualified and experienced Ophthalmologist and paramedics. It has 25200 Sq.ft. built-up area with 72 Bed capacity. The Population coverage is of 3.5 million from seven revenue districts. Since inception, TEH is running a Community Ophthalmic Outreach Programm for the benefit of poorest and downtrodden needy people of our society to serve their primary Eye care at their door step and If in need of further treatment they are brought to our tertiary Eye Care center at Nashik by hospital's own Vehicles, operated with post-op medication, 3 times meal all free of cost.
